SELECT COUNT(*) FROM info_type AS it1, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND  it1.info = 'budget' ;

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM info_type AS it2, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND  it2.info = 'votes' ;
